PrecisEnactment of the REGULATIONS PRESCRIBING CERTAIN FIREARMS AND OTHER WEAPONS, COMPONENTS AND PARTS OF WEAPONS, ACCESSORIES, CARTRIDGE MAGAZINES, AMMUNITION AND PROJECTILES AS PROHIBITED OR RESTRICTED which classify certain firearms and ammunition into the following categories: (1) Prohibited Firearms, (2) Restricted Firearms, (3) Prohibited Weapons, (4) Prohibited Devices, and (5) Prohibited Ammunition, as of October 1, 1998.
